    "body" : "<p>Also I think <em>if_exists</em> was used like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Hi ${userName?if_exists}, How are you?\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>which will not break if userName is null, the result if null would be:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Hi , How are you?\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>if_exists is now deprecated and has been replaced with the default operator ! as in</p>\n\n<pre><code>Hi ${userName!}, How are you?\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>the default operator also supports a default value, such as:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Hi ${userName!\"John Doe\"}, How are you?\n</code></pre>\n"
