    "body" : "<p>This one seems to be a better fit:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;#if userName?has_content&gt;\n... do something\n&lt;/#if&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://freemarker.sourceforge.net/docs/ref_builtins_expert.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://freemarker.sourceforge.net/docs/ref_builtins_expert.html</a></p>\n"
