    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>For versions previous to FreeMarker 2.3.7</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>You can not use <code>??</code> to handle missing values, the old syntax is:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;#if userName?exists&gt;\n   Hi ${userName}, How are you?\n&lt;/#if&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
